{"tid":1426778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大天文學會：唔好撈亂觀星筆同雷射槍","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:36:07.000Z","uid":101392,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37176449468494b696f8681cfff28940ca52c305","tid":1426778,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"天文小知識 - 觀星筆🤩<br />\n<br />\n鐳射筆（Laser pointer），又稱激光筆、觀星筆等，除咗會喺課堂上作為解說工具，更加係天文愛好者嘅常備工具之一，佢喺一般嘅店舖或者網上嘅購物平台都可以輕易入手。觀星筆發出嘅鐳射光可以方便講星者指向天空中唔同嘅天體同星座，令聽眾更容易理解講者所講嘅係邊粒星🌟，藉此加強同聽眾嘅溝通😄！<br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係，本會發現近日觀星筆同極具殺傷力嘅攻擊性武器 - 鐳射槍（Blaster）竟被混為一談🤦🏿&zwj;♂。根據星球大戰百科全書，鐳射槍🔫係一款能量武器，喺銀河系入面被廣泛使用。大多數步兵都係以鐳射槍作為主要武器。<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 為咗方便大眾分辨觀星筆同鐳射槍，本會已經將兩者嘅中、英文名稱附加喺呢篇帖子嘅圖片中，希望有助於各位分辨兩者啦💁🏻&zwj;♂！大家唔好再撈亂啦🌚！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/291114747609745/posts/2272687386119128?s=814165759&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F291114747609745%2Fposts%2F2272687386119128%3Fs%3D814165759%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apADpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=e2fdb8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/291114747609745/posts/2272687386119128?s=814165759&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"14b9a7b2e94c7c16dab9d9bcd91cd045d4725a5b","tid":1426778,"uid":160147,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0xKDKc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0xKDKc.png&h=d203340f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93e0fc376b3ab8a127bb5e998a2e45b4d85ad854","tid":1426778,"uid":126931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"有邊款好介紹呀"},{"pid":"bab1633b72ddc79b8a6b33952f914599a4422ec8","tid":1426778,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93e0fc376b3ab8a127bb5e998a2e45b4d85ad854","tid":1426778,"uid":126931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"有邊款好介紹呀"